{
  "stem": "11179.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We-- we-- we got used to those things, like the dead on the street, dead children they put out in the street to be picked up, dead people in the street to be picked up by the city.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- they called them [NON-ENGLISH], the ones that picked up those pots every day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And people lived on the street, in the summer particularly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was hot in their houses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were crowded, the Chinese now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I don't think it took me very long to not seeing what I didn't want to see.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This is about-- this is about all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I saw it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it-- but it was none of my concern.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My mother had a harder time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My father had less of a hard time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And a lot of people had a-- some people took like duck to the water, they didn't mind it at all.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They figured out a way to make a living.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But not many, I would say-- not too many.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And some gave up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There were those who gave up, even younger people, especially professionals that had absolutely no field there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Like you take attorneys, particular attorneys-- even people who were judges once.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They were somebody once.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Some of them could never accept it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I met in a camp, we lived in a-- when I lived in a camp, we lived-- 30 boys, from seven to 20, in the same room, double beds.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we didn't-- it was nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But after a while, they needed this room for some older people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They mixed them in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Older men in there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was a dumb move, but somebody was in charge to do it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And some of these older people, first of all they were not clean.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They were very unhappy people.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
